2010年，單位顧問委員會在英國召開的會議通過了《國際單位制手冊》的修訂草案，同年呈交至國際度量衡委員會。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bipm.org/utils/en/pdf/24_CGPM_Convocation_Draft_Resolution_A.pdf|title=On the possible future revision of the International System of Units, the SI|last=Mills|first=Ian|publisher=CCU|date=2010-09-29|accessdate=2011-01-01|archive-date=2012-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120113075832/http://www.bipm.org/utils/en/pdf/24_CGPM_Convocation_Draft_Resolution_A.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="draft">{{cite web
